These are Puzzles for 3x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-1::.
City: edinburgh, new-york, venice, nizza, rome, hamburg
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, horse, lizard, rat, snake
House: victorian, ranch-style, futuristic, gothic-revival, colonial, art-deco
 1. the victorian house is the owner of the horse##1
 2. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
 3. the victorian house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 4. the art-deco house is the owner of the snake##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 7. the owner of the snake is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 8. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the person traveling to rome is the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
12. the person traveling to hamburg is between the colonial house and the owner of the goldfish##2
13. the victorian house is between the person traveling to venice and the owner of the rat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |     4      |    5     |     6      |
| City   | nizza | rome  | hamburg  | edinburgh | new-york  | venice   |
| Pet           | lizard | goldfish | snake | rat        | horse    | chinchilla |
| House     | futuristic    | gothic-revival     | art-deco   | colonial       | victorian | ranch-style       |

