.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-2::.
6 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, backgammon, whist, go, bridge
There are 6 different favourite colors: coral, purple, aquamarine, light-blue, blue, orange
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, hedgehog, horse, lizard, turtle
 1. the person who likes coral is the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the person playing bridge is the person who likes blue##1
 3. the person playing whist is the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 5. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who likes coral and the owner of the lizard##2
 8. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 9. the person who likes orange is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
10. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
11. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
12. the person playing backgammon is the owner of the ferret##1
13. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |    5     |     6      |
| Game      | backgammon     | mah-jongg | snooker     | whist    | go | bridge     |
| Color   | coral | purple | light-blue | orange | aquamarine  | blue  |
| Pet           | ferret    | hedgehog    | lizard     | turtle  | horse    | chinchilla |

