 3. the person who likes blue is on the far left##1
 4. the person who likes blue is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the brazilian##1
 7. the egyptian is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the right of the colombian##1
 9. the person who likes blue is the person who likes blue##1
10. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
11. the person who likes brown is between the pakistani and the person driving the train##2
12. the person driving the bus is on the left of the nigerian##1
13. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the pakistani##1
14. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |   6   |
