The people prefer 6 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, climbing, golf, parkour, volleyball
 1. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 4. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 5. the person playing billiard is the person who likes light-blue##1
 6. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1
 8. the person playing snooker is the person who likes grey##1
 9. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
10. the person playing bridge is the person who's sport is parkour##1
11. the person playing go is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing bridge##2
12. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |    4     |     5      |    6    |
| Game   | snooker       | domino   | billiard   | backgammon  | go | bridge   |
| Color           | grey    | lilac    | light-blue | aquamarine      | pink       | turquise  |
