The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: dahlia, balloon-flower, daisy, marigold, bellflower, orchid
 1. the person eating cherry is the person who growsdahlia##1
 2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person eating eggplant is the person playing poker##1
 4. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is the person eating pomegranate##1
 8. the person playing go is between the person eating papaya and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
 9. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
10. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
11. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
12. the person who growsbellflower is the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |    3     |   4    |     5     |    6    |
