 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is between the fan of blues and the craftsman house##2
 9. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
10. the victorian house is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
11. the fan of trance is on the right of the victorian house##1
12. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3      |     4      |     5     |    6    |
| House           | craftsman | farmhouse | futuristic | tower | victorian | art-deco |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | jazz           | blues      | r&b        | gospel    | trance  |
| Color   | mauve | fuchsia     | yellow  | turquise   | grey    | black |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-18::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, fanta, mirinda, cola, juice
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, disco, electronic, house, pop, salsa
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, animation, adventure, martial-arts, family, action
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 3. the person watching comedy movies is the person drinking juice##1
 4. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the fan of house##1
 7. the person drinking cola is the person watching action movies##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is between the person drinking mirinda and the fan of disco##2
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person watching action movies is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
13. the person drinking cola is the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |    5    |     6      |
| Beverage         | mirinda | juice | fanta   | almond-milk    | cola | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | salsa   | disco     | electronic | house   | blues      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | comedy | martial-arts | animation  | action | family    |

