.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-19::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  manager, firefighter, chef, nurse, fisherman, project-manager
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: may, october, april, march, november, july
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: ambient, folk, indie, pop, soul, trance
 1. the fan of indie is on the right of the fisherman##1
 2. the project-manager is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 3. the nurse is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the chef##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the nurse##1
 7. the fan of folk is between the fan of indie and the fan of ambient##2
 8. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
11. the manager is the fan of pop##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
13. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |      4      |     5      |   6    |
| Job          | manager | nurse      | fisherman | chef       | firefighter | project-manager   |
| Birthday         | november | july | april   | may | march    | october  |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | ambient     | folk      | indie       | soul       | trance |

