.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-20::.
House: gothic-revival, craftsman, palace, townhouse, cottage, cape-cod
There 6 different types of food: apple, banana, kiwi, peach, pepper, tomato
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, oliveros, siglo, alhambra, chaman, tiparillo
 1. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating tomato is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 3. the person eating peach is between the cape-cod house and the gothic-revival house##2
 4. the alhambra-smoker is the person eating apple##1
 5. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the cottage house##1
 6. the palace house is between the old-henry-smoker and the townhouse house##2
 7. the cottage house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 8. the old-henry-smoker is the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the cottage house is the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
11. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
12. the person eating tomato is the craftsman house##1
13. the siglo-smoker is the siglo-smoker##1
14. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |    5     |    6     |
| House      | townhouse   | palace | gothic-revival     | cottage     | cape-cod    | craftsman    |
| Food          | pepper   | apple         | banana  | peach   | kiwi     | tomato   |
| Cigar   | chaman | alhambra        | old-henry | tiparillo | siglo | oliveros |

 